description: It is time to take “bad” out of your vocabulary. Chances are, you aren’t bad at Souls games, you’re just impatient. Practicing patience is easier said than done, I know, but I promise you that it's the foundation to being better at games like Elden Ring.
title: You're Not Bad at Elden Ring, Just Impatient

description:
Revered Spirit Ashes serve as your way to level up your Spirit Ashes in the Elden Ring DLC: Shadow of the Erdtree, as well as your way to level up Torrent. Here's a guide on how to find all 24, organized by region:

1-8: Gravesite Plain
9-14: Scadu Altus
15-16: Abyss
17-20: Rauh Ruins
21-24: Enir-Ilim
